articles.title: One of Boston’s two remaining strip clubs wants to move. Chinatown is leery.
articles.description:
Monet doesn’t see what the big deal is. Neither does her fellow exotic dancer, Lexy, nor the host named Jimmy. After all, Centerfolds Boston, one of two remaining strip clubs in downtown Boston, is trying to move just a block away.
